text: Ompundja Constituency is an electoral constituency in the Oshana Region of northern Namibia. It had 4,423 registered voters in 2004. The constituency councillor is SWAPO activist Adolf Hitler UunonaGovernment Gazette of the Republic of Namibia. December 9, 2010, No. 4627 who has been serving in this role since 2004. == Politics == Ompundja constituency is dominated by the South West Africa People's Organization (SWAPO) party of Namibia. In the 2015 local and regional elections the SWAPO candidate won uncontested and became councillor after no opposition party nominated a candidate. ==References== Category:Constituencies of Oshana Region
title: Ompundja Constituency
